---
slug: "cases"
permalink: "/en/cases/index.html"
title: "Ready scenarios: business, family, relocation, groups | Morrison"
description: "5 real transfer configurations with timing, vehicle and reference price. Find yours — we already know how to assemble it."
breadcrumbs:
  - { name: "Home", path: "/en/" }
  - { name: "Scenarios", path: "/en/cases/" }
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <p class="kicker reveal-up">Scenarios</p>
    <h1 class="reveal-up">Ready configurations<br>for common tasks.</h1>
    <p class="lead reveal-up">5 cases we see regularly. If yours is close, we assemble in a day. If different, we assemble to fit.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cases-grid">
      {%- for sc in cases.scenarios %}
      <article class="case-card" id="{{ sc.id }}">
        <p class="case-audience">{{ sc.audience.en }}</p>
        <h2>{{ sc.headline.en }}</h2>
        <p>{{ sc.summary.en }}</p>
        <dl class="case-spec">
          <div><dt>Vehicle</dt><dd>{{ sc.spec.vehicle }}</dd></div>
          <div><dt>Passengers</dt><dd class="num">{{ sc.spec.pax }}</dd></div>
          <div><dt>Duration</dt><dd class="num">{{ sc.spec.duration }}</dd></div>
          <div><dt>Route</dt><dd>{{ sc.spec.route }}</dd></div>
          <div><dt>From</dt><dd class="num">R$ {{ sc.spec.priceFromBrl }}</dd></div>
        </dl>
        <a class="btn btn-dark btn-arrow" href="/en/contact/?case={{ sc.id }}">Request this format</a>
      </article>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--bg-navy">
  <div class="container container--narrow" style="text-align: center;">
    <p class="kicker">Not yours</p>
    <h2>We'll assemble for your case.</h2>
    <p style="max-width: 560px; margin: 1.2rem auto 1.8rem;">Tell us the task — we send back configuration, price and timing in one message.</p>
    <div class="cta-strip-actions" style="justify-content: center;">
      <a class="btn btn-dark btn-arrow" href="/en/contact/">Open the form</a>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="{{ site.contacts.whatsappUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
